snippet: The Mercedes GL350, powered by an awesome 3-liter diesel V-6, is the first rung in the redesigned GL lineup, but you’re welcome to stuff it with nearly all of the options available on the fancier models.
abstract: Behind the Wheel column review of 2013 Mercedes-Benz GL350 Bluetec.
lead_paragraph: The Mercedes GL350, powered by an awesome 3-liter diesel V-6, is the first rung in the redesigned GL lineup, but you’re welcome to stuff it with nearly all of the options available on the fancier models.
